short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Want to know if a Twitter page is using AI content? This extension does just that.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Journey Buster is an extension for scanning Twitter/X posts for AI generated content through manual comparison between our servers hand-reviewed list of known users and will therefore notify you of the nature of the content of these posts.
